text: Sakala Kala Vallabhudu is an Indian Telugu language film directed by Shiva Ganesh, Produced by Anil Kumar Guntreddy under Simha Films banner. It is a commercial mass entertainer setup in a village backdrop film starring Tanishq Reddy, Meghla Mukta in lead roles, while Prudhvi Raj (Telugu actor), Suman (actor), Jeeva (Telugu actor) appears in supporting roles. This movie started its shooting in December 2017 and was released on 1 February 2019. == Plot == Seenu is a happy go lucky youth who falls in love with Chaitra. She is not charmed by the manner of his teasing and she avoids him. Chaitra starts developing a feeling for him, and she is kidnapped. == Cast == * Tanishq Reddy *Suman (actor) * Meghla Mukta * Prudhvi Raj (Telugu actor) * Alexius Macleod * Jabardash Vinod Kumar * Uttej *Jeeva (Telugu actor) * Ananth * Apurva == Soundtrack == Music of the film was composed by Ajay Patnaik, brother of popular music director turned hero R. P. Patnaik. and the audio was released through Mango Music label.
